# Smart-Lender: AI-Based Loan Eligibility Prediction System

## Project Overview
This project is an end-to-end Machine Learning web application designed to automate and streamline the loan approval process. It replaces manual profiling with predictive modeling to instantly determine applicant loan eligibility.

## Key Features
* Automated loan eligibility prediction using machine learning.
* Full-stack web interface for applicant data entry.
* Real-time analysis of applicant criteria.

## Setup Instructions
To run this project locally:

1. **Clone the repository:**
   `git clone https://github.com/nagi2271-ally/Loan-Eligibility-Predictor.git`

2. **Install required libraries:**
   `pip install -r requirements.txt`

3. **Run the application:**
   `python app.py`

## Project Structure
* `app.py`: Main Flask application file.
* `train_model.py`: Script used for training the machine learning model.
* `templates/`: Folder containing HTML files for the web interface.
